<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Future ilomero</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset & base */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    html, body {
      height: 100%;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0f0f, #1a1a1a);
      color: #e2e8f0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Container */
    .future-container {
      max-width: 700px;
      padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.08);
      text-align: center;
      animation: fadeInScale 1.2s ease forwards;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #67e8f9, #38bdf8);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      animation: fadeInUp 1.4s ease forwards;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      animation: fadeInUp 1.6s ease forwards;
      opacity: 0.85;
    }

    .hint {
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #64748b;
      animation: fadeInUp 2s ease forwards;
    }

    /* Animations */
    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      0% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
      }
      100% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    @keyframes fadeInScale {
      0% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: scale(0.95);
      }
      100% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: scale(1);
      }
    }

    /* Glow orb background */
    .glow {
      position: absolute;
      width: 600px;
      height: 600px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, #38bdf8 0%, transparent 70%);
      top: -150px;
      left: -200px;
      filter: blur(80px);
      opacity: 0.2;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
      animation: pulseGlow 6s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }

    @keyframes pulseGlow {
      0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.15; }
      100% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.25; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="glow"></div>

  <div class="future-container">
    <h1>The Future of Ilomero</h1>
    <p>
      In the future, <strong>Ilomero</strong> might return online.<br />
      But if it does, it won’t be the same as before.
    </p>
    <p>
      The original services, style, and features<br />
      will not come back as they once were.
    </p>
    <div class="hint">
      Stay curious. Something new might rise from nothing.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
